channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Trump Appears To Blackout During Interview
item.description: During an interview with former aide Corey Lewandowski, Trump appeared to blackout while discussing Biden potentially being on drugs.

item.title: The Great Paradox: How Unchecked Mass Migration Hurts Migrants
item.description: Pro-mass-migration voices depict mass migration as an unqualified good for everyone involved, minimizing or refusing to even acknowledge negative side effects or costs. item.title: Republicans Are Worried That Trump Will Self-Destruct At The Debate
item.description: Republicans are advising Trump not to be himself, as they are worried about their felon nominee self-destructing on the debate stage with President Biden.

item.title: Speaker Mike Johnson Is Now Trying To Keep Steve Bannon Out Of Prison
item.description: Steve Bannon is supposed to report to prison for contempt of Congress, but Speaker Mike Johnson (R-LA) and House Republican leadership are trying to save him.

item.title: Trump Hid Hundreds Of Chinese Trademarks That He Owns During His Presidency
item.description: As Trump and Biden get ready to debate, it is important to remember that Trump took $5.5 million from the Chinese government and failed to disclose hundreds of Chinese trademarks that he owns.
